high_descs: Take a step to your right then walk to the counter in front of you.
Pick up the spoon that's in front of you. under the yellow handled knife
Take a step to your right so you face the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and walk to the counter then step to your left and walk to the stool then turn right.
Put the spoon on the counter to the left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon on the counter.

high_descs: Take a step to the right and face the counter.
Pick up the spoon from the front of the counter.
Carry the spoon and take a step to the right.
Place the spoon in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the spoon.
Hold the spoon and turn around. Turn to the right to face the island.
Place the spoon in the center of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a spoon and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Walk ahead to the counter to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Take a step right to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Turn around and walk around the left side of the table. Face the table next to the wooden stool.
Place the spoon on the table in front of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spoon on a table.
